{
  "text": "For example, compare the statement of the Neukirch-Ikeda-Uchida theorem in 1.1 with the theorem proved by Mochizuki, cf. Th. 1.9 of [CITATION_1] -III, The number field F can be reconstructed via an algorithmic procedure from the arithmetic fundamental group \u03c0 1 (X F ) (which surjects onto the absolute Galois group G F ).",
